    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/61905f25ec65cbbcb2c45f5d5ebe3174.avif?t=1726154141\" width=640 height=78 /></span><br>Buckle up for an electrifying ride in CyberRush, where Subway Surfer meets the high-speed thrills of NFS! Immerse yourself in the breathtaking landscapes of a procedurally generated Cyberpunk city as you blaze through neon-lit streets in this fusion of infinite runner and racing genres.<br><br>🚗 <strong>Fast-Paced Action</strong>: Get ready for an adrenaline-fueled experience as you maneuver through dynamically generated levels. Speed is your ally, but can you outsmart the relentless police chases and navigate the procedural obstacle course?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/936e21ca5c32889260517ddb16810557.poster.avif?t=1726154141\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/936e21ca5c32889260517ddb16810557.webm?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/936e21ca5c32889260517ddb16810557.mp4?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🌋 <strong>Epic Boss Battles</strong>: Challenge your limits against titanic bosses in intense, adrenaline-fueled epic battles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/19e1718d0ac87b0fa39c3f8a7781a213.poster.avif?t=1726154141\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/19e1718d0ac87b0fa39c3f8a7781a213.webm?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/19e1718d0ac87b0fa39c3f8a7781a213.mp4?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>💥 <strong>Power Ups</strong>: Unleash chaos and speed as you transform into a variety of powerful vehicles with the ultimate power-up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/bc3e669b5eaed98ea1dbd8e9a3c975eb.poster.avif?t=1726154141\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/bc3e669b5eaed98ea1dbd8e9a3c975eb.webm?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/bc3e669b5eaed98ea1dbd8e9a3c975eb.mp4?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🚨 <strong>Hot Pursuit</strong>: It's not just about the race; it's about the chase! Feel the thrill of heart-pounding pursuits as the police relentlessly pursue you. Dodge obstacles, and use power-ups to leave them in the dust.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/ccf03c15c4e4cf49754a4dbe1b376358.poster.avif?t=1726154141\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/ccf03c15c4e4cf49754a4dbe1b376358.webm?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/ccf03c15c4e4cf49754a4dbe1b376358.mp4?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🌆 <strong>Surreal Cyberpunk Setting</strong>: Immerse yourself in the mesmerizing world of CyberRush, featuring stunning Cyberpunk aesthetics. Glide through neon-drenched skyscrapers and city streets as you push your reflexes to the limit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/a801dfd78757a49dedce8a87974842c7.poster.avif?t=1726154141\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/a801dfd78757a49dedce8a87974842c7.webm?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338940/extras/a801dfd78757a49dedce8a87974842c7.mp4?t=1726154141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🏆 <strong>Beat Your Highscore</strong>: Compete against yourself as you strive to beat your high score.<br><br>Get ready for a rush like never before in CyberRush, where the streets are your playground, and every run is a new adventure. Are you up for the challenge? The city awaits your neon-lit fury!",
